{
  "id": "5d71ceae9dafb10017cbf812",
  "title": "反脆弱性",
  "created": 1567739572,
  "updated": 1643345053,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5d71ceae9dafb10017cbf812",
      "text": "反脆弱性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739572,
      "updated": 1567739572
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be7aaff09e00006f2b04",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1c1b24c118fda5b9338bc21bbb530acc][https://gyazo.com/ef840c80e4265ec678680c4d90af9865]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259706,
      "updated": 1568259766
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be7caff09e00006f2b05",
      "text": "\t[Amazon https://amzn.to/2UQpJwW]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259708,
      "updated": 1568259737
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be9aaff09e00006f2b06",
      "text": "\t[ブラックスワン https://amzn.to/2I29xDC]の著者による新作",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259738,
      "updated": 1568259818
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be9aaff09e00006f2b07",
      "text": "\t「不確実な世界を生き延びる唯一の考え方」煽りすぎだね [邦題が変]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259738,
      "updated": 1568259890
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79bf08aff09e00006f2b09",
      "text": "\t\t原題は「Things that gain from disorder」「無秩序から得られるもの」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259848,
      "updated": 1568259964
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79bfcfaff09e00006f2b0c",
      "text": "\t\tこれは反脆弱性が不確実性から得られる利益の量に着目した概念なので真っ当なタイトル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260048,
      "updated": 1568260071
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79bfc4aff09e00006f2b0b",
      "text": "　反脆弱性の定義の前提になる話を[リスクと脆弱性]に書いた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260037,
      "updated": 1643345053
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71cf66aff09e00000b96ab",
      "text": "\t脆弱",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739751,
      "updated": 1568259824
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71cf6faff09e00000b96ae",
      "text": "\t頑健(ロバスト)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739759,
      "updated": 1567739874
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71cfe2aff09e00000b96b0",
      "text": "\t反脆弱",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739874,
      "updated": 1567739878
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71cf66aff09e00000b96ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739751,
      "updated": 1567739751
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f5c5aff09e00000b96b1",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/54b243b6cad056d4c8dc665caa0be55a]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567749574,
      "updated": 1567749575
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f5c7aff09e00000b96b2",
      "text": "\thttps://arxiv.org/pdf/1208.1189.pdf",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567749575,
      "updated": 1567749585
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71cf67aff09e00000b96ad",
      "text": "\t\t従来、不確定性は「害がある」と考えられてきた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739751,
      "updated": 1567750681
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71fa18aff09e0000aa8d0b",
      "text": "\t\t\t不確定性から被る害が大きいものを「脆弱」、小さいものを「頑健」と呼んできた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750681,
      "updated": 1567750681
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f9f5aff09e0000aa8d0a",
      "text": "\t\tしかし、不確定性には害だけでなく益もある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750646,
      "updated": 1567750666
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71fa2daff09e0000aa8d0c",
      "text": "\t\t\t不確定性から得る益の大きいものを「反脆弱」と言う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750701,
      "updated": 1567750716
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f99daff09e0000aa8d08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750557,
      "updated": 1567750557
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f99daff09e0000aa8d09",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750557,
      "updated": 1567750557
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71ceb0aff09e00000b96a8",
      "text": "\tオプション性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739574,
      "updated": 1567739596
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f7ecaff09e00000b96b7",
      "text": "\t\tオプションには価値がある話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750125,
      "updated": 1567750136
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f82aaff09e00000b96ba",
      "text": "\t\t[オプションバリュー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750187,
      "updated": 1567750193
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71ceccaff09e00000b96aa",
      "text": "\tバーベル戦略",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739596,
      "updated": 1567739604
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f7f9aff09e00000b96b8",
      "text": "\t\t限定的リスクをたくさん取ることで、大勝ちから大きな利益を得る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750137,
      "updated": 1567750165
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f81eaff09e00000b96b9",
      "text": "\t\t連想: [リアルオプション]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750174,
      "updated": 1567750182
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71ceccaff09e00000b96a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567739596,
      "updated": 1567739596
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f774aff09e00000b96b3",
      "text": ">タレブの2007年の著書『ブラック・スワン―不確実性とリスクの本質』は、サブプライムローンの破綻がきっかけで起きたリーマンショックのあと、全米で150万部の大ヒットを記録した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750005,
      "updated": 1567750007
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f775aff09e00000b96b4",
      "text": ">タレブは、反脆さとはオプションを持つことだという。「オプションとは私たちを反脆くしてくれるものだ。オプションがあれば、不確実性の負の側面から深刻な害をこうむることなく、不確実性の正の側面から利益を得ることができるのだ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750005,
      "updated": 1567750047
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f778aff09e00000b96b5",
      "text": "\t[メーカーが「反脆さ」を身につけるために必要なことは？ : デザイン思考で行こう！ http://kyosuke.doorblog.jp/archives/5326060.html]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750009,
      "updated": 1567750059
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71f7abaff09e00000b96b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1567750059,
      "updated": 1567750059
    },
    {
      "id": "5d71ff39aff09e00004c32e4",
      "text": "\t[『反脆弱性』で不確実性を味方につける | シゴタノ！ https://cyblog.jp/29059]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
